➜雨停抢收贡米稻
http://www.sohu.com/a/424753428_114731	4597
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201015/a6f7906870be470a974ff6b5bacb2d17.jpeg" width="640" height="426" /></p>
